<table class="row">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td class="wrapper last">
        <table class="twelve columns">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="panel panel-default">

                <table>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="200"></td>
                    <td>
                      <a href="<%= user_url(@invitor, i: @invite.id) %>">
                        <%= image_tag(@invitor.avatar.url(120), width: 60, height: 60, class: 'img-circle') %>
                      </a>
                    </td>
                    <td width="200"></td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <p>Your friend <a href="<%= user_url(@invitor, i: @invite.id) %>">@<%= @invitor.username %></a> is building a product called <%= @product.name %> on Assembly, and thought youâ€™d be a great new member of the team.</p>

                <% if @invite.note.present? %>
                  <blockquote>
                    <span style="font-size: 12px;color:#999">From @<%= @invitor.username %>:</span><br/>
                    <%== markdown @invite.note %>
                  </blockquote>
                <% end %>

                <p>Products on Assembly are built collaboratively, and ownership (along with future revenue) is distributed through App Coins.</p>
                <% if @via.is_a? Task %>
                  <p>You have two initial opportunities to own part of <%= @product.name %> today:</p>

                  <ol>
                    <li>Create an Assembly account and claim the <%= @invite.tip_cents / 100 %> <%= @product.name %> App Coins that <a href="<%= user_url(@invitor, i: @invite.id) %>">@<%= @invitor.username %></a> just tipped to you.</li>

                    <li>Complete the bounty that <a href="<%= user_url(@invitor, i: @invite.id) %>">@<%= @invitor.username %></a> thought you'd be perfect for, which is worth <%= (@via.bounty.total_cents / 100).to_i %> App Coins.</li>
                  </ol>

                  <table class="button success radius">
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <a href="<%= product_wip_url(@product, @via, i: @invite.id) %>">
                          Help @<%= @invitor.username %> build <%= @product.name %>
                        </a>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                <% else %>
                  <p>To get started, create an Assembly account and you'll automatically claim the <%= @invite.tip_cents / 100 %> <%= @product.name %> App Coins that <a href="<%= user_url(@invitor, i: @invite.id) %>">@<%= @invitor.username %></a> just tipped to you.</p>

                  <table class="button success radius">
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <a href="<%= product_url(@product, i: @invite.id) %>">
                          Help @<%= @invitor.username %> build <%= @product.name %>
                        </a>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                <% end %>

                <p>
                  <br/>
                  <a href="<%= faq_url(i: @invite.id) %>">Learn more about Assembly</a><br/>
                  <a href="<%= product_url(@product, i: @invite.id) %>">Learn more about <%= @product.name %></a>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
